  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spikair volleyball is a game where you control the whole team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You choose the players actions within high tension matches where timing is decisive !</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And if you want to play with friends or family, you can go for the co-op or versus mode ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RECRUITING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit new players with better statistics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769270/extras/889919530be04f8e3be66a0d6017de59.poster.avif?t=1771598282\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769270/extras/889919530be04f8e3be66a0d6017de59.webm?t=1771598282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769270/extras/889919530be04f8e3be66a0d6017de59.mp4?t=1771598282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TRAINING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Train your players to build the best team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769270/extras/85e71d68e5f37106cfee06b68e06efe5.poster.avif?t=1771598282\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769270/extras/85e71d68e5f37106cfee06b68e06efe5.webm?t=1771598282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769270/extras/85e71d68e5f37106cfee06b68e06efe5.mp4?t=1771598282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TOURNAMENTS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lead your team to win the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769270/extras/e6788871fbd83ba621cba4a716c02af9.poster.avif?t=1771598282\" width=610 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769270/extras/e6788871fbd83ba621cba4a716c02af9.webm?t=1771598282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769270/extras/e6788871fbd83ba621cba4a716c02af9.mp4?t=1771598282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rise to the top ! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become the best volleyball club of the world.</p>",
